subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson is part of a cosmopolitan growth niche in Nascar that has, for several years now, been expanding beyond its Lynyrd Skynyrd demographics.
